item.title: CVE-2019-10792|2024-08-04T22:32:01.668Z -- snyk -- bodymen
item.description: bodymen before 1.1.1 is vulnerable to Prototype Pollution. The handler function could be tricked into adding or modifying properties of Object.prototype using a __proto__ payload.
